{
  "stem": "3165.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she grabbed us, and she opened the back door, and she let us out fast, before the Gestapo came into the front door.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here again, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] here on the streets, looking again where to hide, where to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And it's getting late at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we're walking, and we're walking, and I think my sister was freezing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] again, I said, well, God again, didn't take me away again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SOBS] I'm on the streets one more time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somehow, as a child, you know, you just-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You go and you-- you know, I think I had my mother in me, because I still continued going and looking where to hide, where do go.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were so tired.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw on a farm a big haystack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said to my sister, let's go into this haystack, make a hole, and we'll sleep over here, because I can't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we went into the haystack and covered ourselves up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then early in the morning, very early in the morning, the farmer, I heard him come with his huge forks, farm forks, to pick hay.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I can hear him going with those forks way down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I motion to my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, cover your eyes, because it's going to poke her-- our eyes out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we both covered our eyes, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we waited for him to get all the hay out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And thank God he never touched us with those huge forks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then it was all quiet, and we heard he left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was daylight now.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
